metadata.name: Princess Raisa
metadata.description:
A Tale of Two Princesses from the “Carbon Grey” graphic novel.

Princess Alena and Raisa – heir to the throne of Ursa. Alena, the true princess, Raisa a servant’s daughter. Once, all they had needed was each other, but those two girls – had both drowned so long ago. Separated by the revolution, the river did what the war could not, and swept the two girls away from each other.

This is Raisa’s story, a servant’s daughter who would one day become the greatest and powerful queen of Ursa.
